      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive reliability and performance. This vehicle has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic. It offers a superior balance of luxury and utility, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to guarantee its readiness for the road. An exceptional acquisition for those who demand quality and value in equal measure.",
