      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a factory 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is optimized for high-revving performance. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including double-VANOS servicing and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing its original MacPherson strut/multi-link configuration for exceptional lateral grip. While presenting with minor aesthetic wear typical of its age, the mechanical integrity is excellent, featuring responsive individual throttle bodies and a linear power band that defines the analog M-car experience.",
